    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# pricing-utils provides editor-level formatting and tier price calculations\n\nLocated at `editors/service-offering-editor/components/pricing-utils.ts`, this module provides UI-level pricing utilities.\n\n## Key Exports\n\n| Function | Purpose | Used By |\n|----------|---------|--------|\n| `formatPrice(amount, currency)` | Currency formatting with symbol | ServiceCatalog, TheMatrix, TierDefinition, TierPricingOptionsPanel |\n| `calculateTierRecurringPrice(groups, cycle, tierId)` | Sum regular group monthly prices for a tier | TierDefinition |\n| `calculateEffectiveSetupPrice(setupCost)` | Apply setup discount, return base/effective/savings | ServiceCatalog, ServiceGroupSetupCostPanel |\n| `detectMajorityCycle(groups, currentCycle, overrides)` | Find majority billing cycle among groups | TheMatrix |\n| `BILLING_CYCLE_LABELS` / `BILLING_CYCLE_SHORT_LABELS` | Human-readable cycle names | Various dropdowns |\n\nRe-exports `BILLING_CYCLE_MONTHS` from the document model.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[helper functions]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:41.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:41.000Z"
    }
  },
